  "detailed_description": "<strong>Desert Kingdoms 2</strong> is a minimal medieval real-time strategy game.<br><br>In the desert there are only a few <strong>waypoints</strong> that can be settled. <br>Conquer these and expand settlements there. <br>Destroy the other kingdoms and become the sole ruler of the desert.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/eae7be5789e304abfcccaa8607fd44b1.poster.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/eae7be5789e304abfcccaa8607fd44b1.webm?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/eae7be5789e304abfcccaa8607fd44b1.mp4?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Manage resources like wood, stone and iron, develop villages, and conquer enemy kingdoms in procedurally generated skirmish maps.<br>Develop cities to build large buildings, like <strong>Siege Workshops</strong>. <br>So you can tear enemy kingdoms apart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/3a2954eb75535537df91ab92c630c6db.poster.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/3a2954eb75535537df91ab92c630c6db.webm?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/3a2954eb75535537df91ab92c630c6db.mp4?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>* <strong>Skirmish mode</strong> with <strong>procedurally generated</strong> maps<br>* Different <strong>unit types</strong> with strengths and weaknesses<br>* Develop villages with different <strong>buildings</strong><br>* <strong>Pause</strong> the game at any time if it gets too hectic or <br>* <strong>speed up time</strong> if you're waiting for something.<br>* <strong>Develop</strong> your settlements from a small hamlet to a village to a city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/5a9fd05c1e7ffae03c9484adfe4c7a11.poster.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/5a9fd05c1e7ffae03c9484adfe4c7a11.webm?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/5a9fd05c1e7ffae03c9484adfe4c7a11.mp4?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hamlet – Village – Town</h2><strong>Hamlet</strong> small settlement with a few building sites where basic resources can be mined<br><br><strong>Village</strong> more space for buildings and special resources. Can mine advanced resources.<br><br><strong>City</strong> Space for large buildings, but unable to mine resources<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/02dd12e4f854204d860e6d260eabde79.poster.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/02dd12e4f854204d860e6d260eabde79.webm?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/02dd12e4f854204d860e6d260eabde79.mp4?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defend settlements from marauding hordes and enemy attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/a47854061363c3cc62924eb23ac28bdc.poster.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/a47854061363c3cc62924eb23ac28bdc.webm?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/a47854061363c3cc62924eb23ac28bdc.mp4?t=1750875402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/aa22fa1feb958e51d1c316d439995a6e.avif?t=1750875402\" width=600 height=192 /></span>",
